entries.femaleVariant: So, I... You want what exactly?
You actually sell meds... outta this place...?
Well... call it a recent change. Used to work in electronics, didn't exactly pan out, had to shift my focus somewhere.
But hey, it's all legit. I took a first aid course on the Net, bought a shard on pharmacy basics. Good to go, choomba. Hey, just let me know what you need.
